# Example crontab entry for the nightly live integration test.
#
# Install on the broker host (or wherever the broker source + venv lives):
#   crontab -e
# then paste the line below (uncommented). Verify with:
#   crontab -l
# Inspect run history:
#   tail -50 ~/jobd/logs/live-test.log
#
# Daily at 04:17 local — off-peak, away from the worker's nightly idle
# checkpoint windows. Adjust if you have other 4am cron jobs.

# 17 4 * * * /opt/jobd/scripts/run-live-test.sh
